We have had a great day with @StBartsTrust for their 2nd Evidence Exploration Partnership workshop. 

Drilling down into a range of data sources to identify a priority. 

@AspirerRS @J0GOODMAN

@TEDxMelbourne #TEDTalkWeek highlight:
Can a cup of coffee change lives? Rebecca Scott, founder of 
@STREAT shows how sustainable choices impact lives, creates jobs for homeless youth & sources coffee ethically. Watch here youtube.com/watch?v=y9aw... #CoffeeWithImpact

Newly passed CA housing reforms (streamline development & use wildfire-ravaged lots for low-income housing) are marketed as improving affordability. But they highlight deep systemic failure: climate change is impacting land, weather, & housing.

